 John,

 https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.source4industries.com/products/10-mold-on-rubber-cast-iron-wheel-2-1-2-wide-1000-lbs-capacity?variant=31080908324909__;!!DxUUcJeb!dkvVl53JjTPanc22jx1aA6j0AzmE66iDTFDuxgJHdOFaOHBoexas6hKQuBb69kM_$

 The cost slightly varies depending on the bearing size. If you're able to measure the diameter of the axles, we can get a proper quote much faster. In order to get a freight quote, I would need the shipping address.
 
 If you would rather get this info on your own without waiting to hear back from me, you can add 4 of each wheel with the correct bearing to your cart, and the first part of the checkout process gathers your shipping information to provide a shipping quote. You can stop there if you're just looking for the final cost, or continue to place the order.
 
 Unfortunately, we don't offer cotter pins, but they should be easy to find at any local hardware store.
 
 Thank you for reaching out to us, and please let me know if there's anything else I can do for you.
